# Books CRUD API – Endpoints

Base URL
http://localhost:9090

1. Add Book (POST)
   http://localhost:9090/addbook

2. Get All Books (GET)
   http://localhost:9090/allbooks

3. Get Book By ID (GET)
   http://localhost:9090/bookid/{bookid}

Example:
http://localhost:9090/bookid/1

4. Update Book (PUT)
   http://localhost:9090/updatebook

5. Delete Book (DELETE)
   http://localhost:9090/bookid/{bookid}

Example:
http://localhost:9090/bookid/1
